===========Database Operations (MongoDB Shell)
// Show all databases
show dbs
Or 
show databases
// Create/switch to database (created when first document is inserted)
use myDatabase

// Check current database (pointer)
db

// Delete current database
db.dropDatabase()
========Creating a Database
// Switch to a database (creates it if it doesn't exist)
//Actually Creating the Database (by inserting data)
use myNewDatabase
// Check current database (db pointer to current database)
db

// List all databases (only shows databases with content)
show dbs
==========Database Stats
// Get database statistics
db.stats()

// Get storage size info
db.storageSize()

==========Dropping a Database
// First switch to the database
use databaseToDelete

// Then drop it
db.dropDatabase()

